*[[義]] - '''Gi''' - [[Rectitude]] (Right Decisions)
*[[勇]] - '''Yu''' - [[Courage]]
*[[仁]] - '''Jin''' - [[benevolence]]
*[[礼]] - '''Rei''' - [[respect]]
*[[誠]] - '''Makoto''' - [[Honesty]]
*[[名誉]] - '''Meiyo''' - [[Honour]]
*[[忠義]] - '''Chugi''' - [[Loyalty]]
